WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.760
Well, good evening, family.

00:00:01.760 --> 00:00:04.320
Thank you for joining me again tonight.

00:00:04.320 --> 00:00:10.675
I want to go over what the Lord showed me real fast yesterday about the towers.

00:00:10.675 --> 00:00:14.440
There was a lot the Lord showed us yesterday, son.

00:00:17.320 --> 00:00:24.240
I want to show you this article real quick from Russia and what they said they want to do.

00:00:24.240 --> 00:00:26.526
It’s interesting.

00:00:26.526 --> 00:00:32.380
I told you Venezuela and Russia will become friends in the days ahead.

00:00:32.380 --> 00:00:34.700
I've told you this over and over again.

00:00:34.700 --> 00:00:49.885
I said Venezuela will be handed a lifeline from Russia to join the BRICS—to join the superpowers of the world because of oil and Venezuela and the visions in the past.

00:00:49.885 --> 00:01:02.448
I said they will back Russia's oil reserves and the things going on with Russia for their economy, and this would be an extension to them.

00:01:02.448 --> 00:01:12.040
So we see Russia saying today that they're open to sending hypersonic missiles to Venezuela.

00:01:13.880 --> 00:01:16.600
I wonder why?

00:01:16.600 --> 00:01:32.251
Well, because I told you in the visions yesterday that I saw that the Venezuelan prime minister will end up being a Saddam Hussein, and it will be like it was in Iraq; it would be its type and shadow.

00:01:38.040 --> 00:01:40.640
I thought that was kind of interesting.

00:01:40.640 --> 00:01:52.891
So now we also see that election anxiety triggers a $100 million wave of NYC buyers heading south.

00:01:53.217 --> 00:01:55.577
People want to head south.

00:01:55.577 --> 00:01:57.489
People are wanting to leave New York.

00:01:57.489 --> 00:01:59.920
And I told you what I saw.

00:01:59.920 --> 00:02:02.400
It wouldn't just be New York.

00:02:02.400 --> 00:02:13.480
In the days ahead, I saw Pennsylvania, I saw a lot of upper East states—far Northeast states—would start to migrate.

00:02:13.480 --> 00:02:25.104
The Christian families in those states, and non-Christians, trying to leave those areas saying, 'We want to relocate.

00:02:25.104 --> 00:02:26.080
We're done.

00:02:26.080 --> 00:02:40.812
' And so I saw a lot of that happening over the next year or two, people trying to really flee those areas because of riots there and because of all the things that the Lord has showed me.

00:02:40.812 --> 00:02:43.360
You know, I know we can stop a lot of this through prayer.

00:02:43.360 --> 00:02:54.006
We're going to pray, but I know that a lot of people are wanting to seek a better opportunity for their families, especially in school districts and liberals.

00:02:54.006 --> 00:03:00.600
And especially, isn't it interesting how that man came out so strong about who he really is?

00:03:00.600 --> 00:03:07.320
And that's the reason for the title of the video today: 'You'll get what you asked for, but it's not what you thought.

00:03:07.320 --> 00:03:10.320
' And that's to the people of New York.

00:03:10.320 --> 00:03:11.280
You'll get it.

00:03:11.280 --> 00:03:30.120
I saw him winning and I even saw him standing in New York Times Square as I saw the flash of light with the two men standing there from CNN, and that man was standing on stage at the New Year's Eve thing.

00:03:30.467 --> 00:03:33.987
I thought that was interesting because I knew he'd win.

00:03:33.987 --> 00:03:41.220
I told Braden, 'You know, even in the prophetic words, I told you all I was saying that basically New York's in trouble.

00:03:41.220 --> 00:03:47.951
' And I saw what David Wilkerson had prophesied was going to start to come to pass.

00:03:47.951 --> 00:03:55.760
The things that we have seen will start to pan out over the city of New York.

00:03:56.036 --> 00:04:00.817
A lot of people, it's going to be a ground of great testing and shaking.

00:04:01.200 --> 00:04:09.954
So, like I said, I don't come on here trying to bring fear, but I try to tell you what's coming and what the Lord has showed us.

00:04:10.693 --> 00:04:19.200
I'm going to go over the building that I saw, and it wasn't the Hudson.

00:04:19.200 --> 00:04:27.514
In my mind, I only see the Hudson River because I thought that was the only river, out of ignorance of what flows through New York.

00:04:27.514 --> 00:04:30.000
But it's the East River.

00:04:30.000 --> 00:04:40.240
So in the vision last night, I saw the East River, which my son said, 'The Hudson's over here, Daddy.

00:04:40.240 --> 00:04:41.590
The East River is right here.

00:04:41.590 --> 00:04:46.573
' So in the vision, I'm seeing the East River, and I called out the Hudson.

00:04:46.573 --> 00:04:47.660
So that's my mistake.

00:04:47.660 --> 00:04:51.160
I'm going to tell you that immediately.

00:04:51.160 --> 00:04:53.760
The East River is right here.

00:04:53.760 --> 00:04:58.220
I see Central Park up here.

00:04:58.220 --> 00:05:03.920
I see the East River and I see the building that's all glass.

00:05:05.760 --> 00:05:10.249
That was a strategic location for this attack that I saw.

00:05:19.568 --> 00:05:32.480
In between the East River and the garden is one of Trump's towers.

00:05:32.480 --> 00:05:43.080
And when I was looking at the building on fire, it was on the northeastern side.

00:05:44.020 --> 00:05:51.160
The fire and the explosion exploded all the way around and it caught the whole thing.

00:05:51.160 --> 00:05:56.420
It looked like 9/11 with the plane, but I don't know what caused the fire.

00:05:56.420 --> 00:06:18.080
I still don't, as I'm praying into this, but this is something that I want you to pray with me because I believe what the Lord showed me: I saw people on barges shooting some kind of rocket launcher or some kind of man-made device at this building.

00:06:18.080 --> 00:06:23.893
Well, this building is close enough to that river; it's right there.

00:06:23.893 --> 00:06:33.827
And as I was looking at everything on fire up top, if you go back to the prophetic word, the word of the Lord said, 'This is a distraction.

00:06:33.827 --> 00:06:41.990
This is not the main event; this is a distraction from what they're really going to try to do.

00:06:42.000 --> 00:06:55.200
' And as I was praying into this last night, the Lord showed me—because I was asking him, 'Lord, show us the date'—and he said, 'You ask a lot.

00:06:55.200 --> 00:07:00.880
' He doesn't want me to share that kind of stuff on YouTube.

00:07:00.880 --> 00:07:10.320
So he took me because he knows I love George Washington Carver and the book 'The Man Who Talks to the Flowers.

00:07:10.320 --> 00:07:12.480
' It's one of my favorite books.

00:07:17.280 --> 00:07:21.800
George Washington Carver asked, 'Show me what's about the peanut.

00:07:21.800 --> 00:07:26.200
' He goes, 'Go back and ask smaller, simpler questions.

00:07:28.640 --> 00:07:31.630
You're asking too much of a complex question.

00:07:31.630 --> 00:07:36.330
' He was saying, 'You need to think different.

00:07:46.800 --> 00:07:47.893
Go at this a different way.

00:07:47.893 --> 00:07:55.160
' It was the way he talked to George Washington Carver because I said, 'Lord, I want a deeper relationship with you.

00:07:55.160 --> 00:07:59.800
I want to hear you more intimately.

00:07:59.800 --> 00:08:02.410
I want to have more fellowship.

00:08:02.410 --> 00:08:07.072
' So here we are.

00:08:21.040 --> 00:08:22.440
We're going to pray tonight.

00:08:22.720 --> 00:08:24.630
I pray about the buildings.

00:08:24.630 --> 00:08:33.909
I pray about what I saw about Japan and South Korea and the Sooners.

00:08:33.909 --> 00:08:58.080
I went over that and I tried to tell you all about the Sooners and about the groundbreaking for Japan to have a crypto-backed currency that was backed by a certain cryptocurrency that would be part of their portfolio.

00:09:05.030 --> 00:09:07.190
It was the same thing with South Korea.

00:09:07.730 --> 00:09:15.200
In the days ahead, you would see Japan and South Korea become more crypto-friendly.

00:09:19.058 --> 00:09:25.840
Then the Lord had us praying over Iraq and he showed me the three men again.

00:09:26.520 --> 00:09:33.720
I saw the hydrocarbon law, the HCL, and Article 140.

00:09:33.720 --> 00:09:55.560
Praying over Article 140 for the distribution of wealth to the people of Iraq so that these three men that are hoarding the money from Iraq would reinstate their currency and bring it back to the way it should be for the Iraqi people.

00:09:55.560 --> 00:10:07.400
There are many avenues, in my opinion, that God wants to use to establish wealth for His people.

00:10:07.400 --> 00:10:09.720
There are many avenues.

00:10:09.720 --> 00:10:30.920
Now, I know there are many scams and things the enemy has tried to use to snare people, but I believe legitimately that God will reveal secret things, hidden things, and treasures of the deep to establish wealth for His people so that we don't lack any good thing.

00:10:30.920 --> 00:10:32.707
Do I believe that could be the Iraqi dinar?

00:10:32.707 --> 00:10:35.027
I have prayed over it for a long time.

00:10:35.027 --> 00:10:39.205
That is not investment advice; I'm not telling you to buy it.

00:10:39.669 --> 00:10:50.320
I'm just telling you I have prayed over the Iraqi dinar a lot, and the Lord has me interceding for that because there's great corruption in the country.

00:10:51.160 --> 00:11:01.040
It's not always about the people becoming filthy rich; it's about establishing a better tomorrow for the people of Iraq, too.

00:11:02.695 --> 00:11:06.067
They live in poverty and destitute situations.

00:11:06.067 --> 00:11:08.640
These people need some relief.

00:11:08.640 --> 00:11:17.260
They can't even have electricity on all the time because of how bad it is over there.

00:11:20.280 --> 00:11:21.480
Our troops are still over there, and we pray for them.

00:11:21.480 --> 00:11:29.360
There are a lot of things involving our bases, but there are just a lot of things the Lord has me praying over.

00:11:29.360 --> 00:11:37.620
One of the things I was interceding for last night was Rockefeller Center this month.

00:11:37.620 --> 00:11:49.280
In the next couple of weeks, for the lighting of the tree when everybody gets together at Rockefeller Center, usually right after Thanksgiving.

00:11:49.672 --> 00:11:52.860
We pray over that, New Year's Eve, and for the parade.

00:11:52.860 --> 00:11:58.120
There are a lot of major events taking place in the next four or five weeks.

00:12:02.543 --> 00:12:08.480
The building I believe the Lord showed me last night was Trump Tower.

00:12:08.480 --> 00:12:09.950
That's just the way it looked to me.

00:12:09.950 --> 00:12:17.554
Now, it could have been Central Park Tower or something like that, but there was another tower that looked very similar.

00:12:20.190 --> 00:12:24.787
It's all right next to that big river and Central Park.

00:12:26.248 --> 00:12:29.679
All I know is the enemy has a plan, but God has a greater plan.

00:12:31.578 --> 00:12:33.903
We are able to see Central Park Tower; it's a beautiful building.

00:12:41.280 --> 00:12:45.720
I'll tell you this: it was the 40th floor.

00:12:50.620 --> 00:12:54.670
I probably said too much, but that's the number that came up in my spirit when I was praying.

00:12:54.670 --> 00:12:56.887
Why the 40th floor?

00:12:56.887 --> 00:13:01.440
If Homeland Security ever sees this, I know I have people watching me all the time now.

00:13:01.440 --> 00:13:07.990
It was the 40th and 41st floors.

00:13:10.480 --> 00:13:14.450
That's what the Lord said to me; I heard that very loud.

00:13:25.669 --> 00:13:26.086
I thought that was interesting.

00:13:33.448 --> 00:13:38.440
Hopefully, that will help somebody praying over our TSA.

00:13:54.240 --> 00:13:54.516
We need the people who check the bags at the airports to get back to work before the Thanksgiving break.

00:13:55.893 --> 00:13:58.776
We need them working; we need our government back open.

00:13:58.776 --> 00:14:14.390
I saw that because people weren't working and there was a gap, they would try to pull something off in this timeframe.

00:14:20.183 --> 00:14:28.044
South Korea—the Lord showed that South Korea would be a place where you can touch down and then distribute the gospel throughout all of Asia.

00:14:32.232 --> 00:14:43.474
The enemy would try to come in and cause havoc in South Korea with communism and try to disrupt the flow of the gospel.

00:14:46.079 --> 00:14:50.771
It is about to take place that it would be an end-time hub, along with Taiwan.

00:14:50.771 --> 00:14:56.674
That's why they're being picked on so much, because they're more free.

00:15:07.007 --> 00:15:18.120
The Lord showed me we must pray for Taiwan and South Korea to remain strong and be pillars in this end-time army spreading the gospel into North Korea, China, and Vietnam.

00:15:18.120 --> 00:15:19.943
It's a great place because, with Dr.

00:15:19.943 --> 00:15:30.520
Cho and other churches there, it's a hub to bring forth the gospel throughout Asia.

00:15:30.820 --> 00:15:39.920
The Lord showed me that the enemy was trying to get a stronghold in their government to transform it into communism, like North Korea and China.

00:15:40.480 --> 00:15:42.189
That was interesting.

00:15:42.189 --> 00:15:48.160
Two weeks ago in Europe, 40,000 SIM cards were found.

00:15:58.413 --> 00:16:01.720
I knew they were establishing something in Europe.

00:16:03.253 --> 00:16:13.194
I don't know if this is part of a terrorist organization, but it's interesting that Homeland Security is busting these people with 40,000 cards.

00:16:22.768 --> 00:16:26.160
They're ransacking their stuff.

00:16:26.160 --> 00:16:31.040
It's a network of communication.

