Do you understand this is encrypted?

00:16:35.417 --> 00:16:44.960
This is well-thought-out, but there are four other places in America just like the New York and New Jersey area where they found over 100,000.

00:16:46.240 --> 00:16:56.400
The Lord said there are four other areas in America—cities like Seattle—that have a network of this.

00:17:03.462 --> 00:17:07.640
I thought it was interesting as we prayed that there were more SIM cards, similar to what happened in New York back in September.

00:17:18.819 --> 00:17:19.224
When they raided before the UN meetings, there were 100,000 SIM cards.

00:17:21.520 --> 00:17:27.011
The Lord said there are more SIM cards in other apartment buildings across the United States for an underground communication system.

00:17:36.200 --> 00:17:36.583
I'm praying our people will find these buildings or apartment complexes and bring these people to justice.

00:17:46.290 --> 00:17:46.500
It's well-funded, obviously.

00:18:00.486 --> 00:18:03.400
So let's pray tonight.

00:18:05.583 --> 00:18:06.971
I won't keep you long.

00:18:09.178 --> 00:18:15.640
I tried to keep it shorter so you could pray longer with me.

00:18:15.830 --> 00:18:18.440
Father, we thank You for the body.

00:18:18.440 --> 00:18:29.640
We thank You for all You've done and continue to do to uncover the darkness in the United States and around the world.

00:18:30.080 --> 00:18:37.372
I thank You for the glorious light, for the light has come and the glory of the Lord has risen upon us.

00:18:37.679 --> 00:18:43.360
I thank You for Your mercy and how good You've been to us.

00:18:43.360 --> 00:18:55.440
Thank You for the Holy Spirit and fire in our lives, that You stir us up from the top of our heads to the soles of our feet, and out of our bellies will flow rivers of living water.

00:18:55.440 --> 00:19:01.413
I thank You for the anointing of the Holy Ghost that flows inside us and reaches the lost.

00:19:01.413 --> 00:19:06.820
I thank You that we are the light right now and that when people see us, they are attracted.

00:19:06.820 --> 00:19:08.660
They say, "What's different about them?

00:19:09.027 --> 00:19:12.200
" We're not just normal; we're church unusual.

00:19:12.200 --> 00:19:15.760
We're unusual, but we stay full.

00:19:15.760 --> 00:19:25.595
That was the main thing the Lord said today: "Tell my people to stay full in these end times.

00:19:25.595 --> 00:19:32.787
" They must remain full of the word of God and my presence.

00:19:32.787 --> 00:19:40.679
They cannot afford in the natural to let their cup not run over.

00:19:40.679 --> 00:19:47.666
They must have a conscience like a drive.

00:19:47.666 --> 00:19:50.600
How bad do you want this?

00:19:50.600 --> 00:19:58.270
How hungry and desperate are you to remain full in these last days?

00:19:58.280 --> 00:20:03.040
It's not just going to happen; you're going to have to put some effort into it.

00:20:03.320 --> 00:20:06.560
The Lord said people must remain full.

00:20:06.560 --> 00:20:27.205
So, Father, I thank you that we are a people remaining full—not just full of what, but filled with and controlled by the Holy Spirit and the word of God, so that we have an overflow and when people see us, they see Jesus in us.

00:20:30.080 --> 00:20:33.680
I thank you, Lord, for the Holy Ghost and fire.

00:20:33.680 --> 00:20:43.520
Father, you are causing us to go up higher with the fire and the glory of the Lord.

00:20:43.742 --> 00:20:46.291
We take the body, Father, and lift it up before you.

00:20:46.549 --> 00:20:55.840
We thank you, Lord, that by your stripes we are healed, whole, and well in the name of Jesus.

00:20:56.130 --> 00:21:07.297
We apply the blood over our households, our children, my wife, my children, our finances, our home, our car, and whatever we may have.

00:21:08.015 --> 00:21:11.160
I plead the blood even over the dogs.

00:21:11.160 --> 00:21:17.990
I thank you, Lord, that whatever we put our hands to will prosper.

00:21:18.240 --> 00:21:25.280
Father, if there's government employees watching this tonight, I thank you that you're their great supply.

00:21:25.280 --> 00:21:34.000
If they've been laid off right now and they don't have jobs because of the government shutdown in America, I thank you, Father, that you will supply for them.

00:21:34.000 --> 00:21:36.960
They'll lack no good thing.

00:21:37.143 --> 00:21:42.815
I thank you, Lord, for your supernatural hand on this house, your goodness, and your mercy.

00:21:45.150 --> 00:21:50.560
We plead the blood over their homes and they will fear not, for you are with them.

00:21:50.800 --> 00:21:54.880
We take this body right now in Jesus' name.

00:21:54.880 --> 00:21:58.430
Go tell your mama to come here.

00:21:58.440 --> 00:22:02.470
Thank you, son.

00:22:03.400 --> 00:22:05.240
Father, we thank you for the blood.

00:22:07.840 --> 00:22:11.160
What can wash away my sin?

00:22:11.160 --> 00:22:15.960
Nothing but the blood of Jesus.

00:22:15.960 --> 00:22:19.760
What can make me whole again?

00:22:19.760 --> 00:22:25.550
Nothing but the blood of Jesus.

00:22:25.560 --> 00:22:29.640
We thank you for the blood; we make much of the blood.

00:22:30.528 --> 00:22:32.470
I want you to pray with me.

00:22:33.448 --> 00:22:35.560
Help bring some push.

00:22:35.560 --> 00:22:37.040
I thank you for the blood.

00:22:40.880 --> 00:22:41.137
I hear you.

00:22:41.137 --> 00:22:43.600
Come over here and sit by me.

00:22:43.600 --> 00:22:48.427
"Baby, I don't have makeup on right now.

00:22:48.427 --> 00:22:52.067
" It does not matter; you're beautiful no matter what.

00:22:59.480 --> 00:22:59.640
We take the blood and apply it, and the blood makes much of us.

00:23:14.424 --> 00:23:15.117
Go around the other side.

00:23:15.117 --> 00:23:16.501
Okay.

00:23:16.501 --> 00:23:20.679
We take the blood right now in Jesus' name.

00:23:20.679 --> 00:23:21.730
Your holy blood, Father.

00:23:21.730 --> 00:23:27.840
We thank you for the blood right now.

00:23:27.840 --> 00:23:31.480
Amen and amen.

00:23:42.560 --> 00:23:42.857
You take the blood.

00:23:42.857 --> 00:23:49.664
There you go, sit right there by me.

00:24:00.433 --> 00:24:00.695
She said, "I don't have any makeup on; I don't want to do this.

00:24:01.218 --> 00:24:06.200
" I said, "Well, no, I didn't say I didn't want to do this, silly.

00:24:06.200 --> 00:24:07.520
" She looks beautiful regardless.

00:24:07.888 --> 00:24:13.648
I told her, "Come over here with or without makeup, I don't care.

00:24:13.648 --> 00:24:14.679
It's fine.

00:24:14.679 --> 00:24:16.280
" "You want a drink?

00:24:16.280 --> 00:24:17.740
" "No, I'm good.

00:24:17.740 --> 00:24:19.720
" Is she in the shot?

00:24:19.720 --> 00:24:21.017
Come on over.

00:24:21.017 --> 00:24:23.020
I'll just stay over here.

00:24:23.020 --> 00:24:25.909
Oh, Father, we just thank you for the blood.

00:24:29.716 --> 00:24:29.933
I depend on her a lot.

00:24:29.933 --> 00:24:31.240
She helps me push.

00:24:35.544 --> 00:24:42.349
I feel her when she's here and when she's not.

00:24:42.349 --> 00:24:48.480
I'm struggling tonight a little, and I told her I need my friend.

00:24:48.480 --> 00:24:49.480
"I'll help you.

00:24:49.480 --> 00:24:49.880
" Yes.

00:24:49.880 --> 00:24:53.658
Well, we've got work to do.

00:24:53.658 --> 00:25:11.240
There are a lot of times when you're pushing like this in the spirit realm—like yesterday, that was a lot of heavy lifting—and I got to get more full.

00:25:11.240 --> 00:25:17.240
That's why he said in the car, when I was in there, "Tell my people to remain full.

00:25:29.091 --> 00:25:29.257
" I was out there vacuuming out Megan's stuff for food, and he said, "They're not remaining full enough.

00:25:29.257 --> 00:25:33.931
" So I took that; he was talking to me, too.

00:25:35.195 --> 00:25:36.840
He said, "Tell my people to remain more full.

00:25:36.840 --> 00:25:43.320
Get more full in the word.

00:25:43.320 --> 00:25:44.480
Get more full of my presence.

00:25:47.240 --> 00:25:49.240
You cannot operate halfway full, empty, or even a quarter full from the top.

00:25:50.200 --> 00:25:55.980
You must always remain full for what's coming.

00:25:55.980 --> 00:26:09.589
You cannot be effective in this spirit realm by being just a little bit full, where you might be a quarter of the way to the top.

00:26:09.589 --> 00:26:12.000
" The Lord said, "You must remain full.

00:26:12.000 --> 00:26:13.737
" That's what he was saying.

00:26:13.971 --> 00:26:23.480
I thought that was interesting as we came home from church tonight and I was praying over everything.

00:26:23.480 --> 00:26:27.829
Even what Pastor Chip was talking about...

00:26:30.411 --> 00:26:36.189
