00:26:41.029 --> 00:26:45.120
Now my mind went blank about what he said, and that's embarrassing as all get-out.

00:26:45.120 --> 00:26:54.920
So if you're watching, Pastor Chip, I was listening and now I'm going to get scolded for not paying attention in class.

00:26:54.920 --> 00:26:56.840
