00:26:56.840 --> 00:26:57.993
Father, I just thank you.

00:27:00.154 --> 00:27:00.291
He talked about Mark Hankins and everything else tonight.

00:27:00.566 --> 00:27:23.110
I remember hearing everything he was saying, and then he called on me—probably because I put my head on your shoulder and he thought I was trying to go to sleep—and he said, "Brandon, do you remember this?

00:27:30.240 --> 00:27:30.396
" I said, "Yes, sir, I remember it.

00:27:30.396 --> 00:27:36.304
" He goes, "How many times does the Lord talk to you in a week?

00:27:36.304 --> 00:27:43.640
" I said, "Well, he talks to me almost every day.

00:27:43.640 --> 00:27:48.978
" You see, Brandon gets to talk to the Lord every day.

00:27:48.978 --> 00:27:57.400
I was putting my head on Diana's shoulder like that, and he probably thought I was falling asleep in church.

00:27:57.400 --> 00:28:00.585
But I wasn't; I was listening.

00:28:04.891 --> 00:28:05.246
I was just loving my wife.

00:28:07.507 --> 00:28:08.711
I love the Lord and I love having fun.

00:28:18.737 --> 00:28:18.954
If you can't have fun in church, then why go?

00:28:34.275 --> 00:28:34.460
You got to have fun and enjoy life.

00:28:34.460 --> 00:28:38.000
Life is too short not to laugh a little.

00:28:39.982 --> 00:28:41.972
I told D, "We need to laugh more.

00:28:48.983 --> 00:28:49.177
" You find something fun and enjoy watching something together and just laughing.

00:28:49.177 --> 00:29:01.173
Life is so serious and sober, the grind of life, trying to make money to pay bills and raising kids.

00:29:02.765 --> 00:29:03.914
You just want to have fun.

00:29:03.914 --> 00:29:06.428
Just laugh a little bit.

00:29:06.428 --> 00:29:08.206
Have an ice cream.

00:29:08.206 --> 00:29:10.020
Is my shirt see-through?

00:29:10.020 --> 00:29:14.312
No, because the green's green and I'm wearing green.

00:29:14.312 --> 00:29:17.457
Are you in the forest?

00:29:21.440 --> 00:29:28.204
I didn't know if I was a floating head because I have this green on today and there's a green screen.

00:29:28.204 --> 00:29:34.108
Diana has a green screen shirt on.

00:29:44.545 --> 00:29:44.730
I just wondered if I was a floating head.

00:29:44.730 --> 00:29:45.655
Good to know.

00:29:45.655 --> 00:29:53.303
Well, if she can wear that, I'll wear one of my green shirts.

00:29:53.303 --> 00:29:56.926
It depends on how dark it is.

00:29:56.926 --> 00:30:02.771
If it's bright, then I put the blue on because I was wearing green.

00:30:10.909 --> 00:30:13.330
I love green, but I don't wear it anymore because I wear a green screen and I'll be a part of the forest.

00:30:21.383 --> 00:30:21.640
All right.

00:30:21.640 --> 00:30:23.737
We've got to be serious here.

00:30:23.737 --> 00:30:28.036
Father, I thank you for the blood.

00:30:30.382 --> 00:30:30.844
We just worship you, Father.

00:30:46.360 --> 00:30:46.610
And we thank you, Father, that we remain full.

00:30:46.860 --> 00:30:48.596
Thank you for our pastors.

00:30:48.596 --> 00:30:52.547
Thank you, Father, for people who feed us spiritually.

00:30:52.547 --> 00:31:03.240
Thank you, God, for all the people that you've put in leadership and positions of authority over the body of Christ.

00:31:03.240 --> 00:31:11.800
Father, we raise up and we become bolder about who we are and what we're called to do.

00:31:11.800 --> 00:31:17.004
Thank you, Father, for this position of leading people in prayer.

00:31:17.333 --> 00:31:26.190
I can't do it without you, Father; I can't do any of this without you.

00:31:31.569 --> 00:31:34.013
You know, I say it all the time: without the Holy Spirit spark, we can't do anything without Jesus.

00:31:36.615 --> 00:31:36.822
We need him, that Holy Ghost fire.

00:31:36.822 --> 00:31:37.858
It's okay, son.

00:31:40.920 --> 00:31:41.110
That's too much noise.

00:31:41.110 --> 00:31:48.627
Father, I thank you for the Holy Ghost and fire, for the glory of the Lord rising up on us.

00:31:48.627 --> 00:31:57.160
Father, I thank you, Lord, for every person represented here tonight, for that fire and that Holy Ghost spark inside of them.

00:31:57.160 --> 00:32:11.365
Father, when they go into their jobs or whatever they're called to do—they could be a security guard, they could be a nurse, or a doctor—I thank you, Father, that they're the best at what they do.

00:32:11.365 --> 00:32:16.048
Father, I thank you, Lord, for that anointing that is to get the job done.

00:32:16.048 --> 00:32:18.253
Father, you teach us all things.

00:32:18.253 --> 00:32:22.787
That's what he was talking about tonight: that, Father, he teaches us in all things.

00:32:22.787 --> 00:32:28.011
He will teach us and we will be the best.

00:32:28.011 --> 00:32:33.560
But it's not just about the word; we would be educated about all things.

00:32:35.040 --> 00:32:44.526
The Holy Spirit will teach us all things, all truth, all blessing, all of it, so that we don't lack any good thing.

00:32:57.351 --> 00:32:57.520
And I thank you, Father, that that's the kind of God we serve.

00:32:57.520 --> 00:33:01.440
They may be a tractor mechanic and they'll be the greatest tractor mechanic that's ever been.

00:33:01.440 --> 00:33:17.340
I don't know why I said that, but I believe I saw a tractor mechanic when I was praying right there in the vision: somebody working on a John Deere tractor.

00:33:17.340 --> 00:33:23.200
I saw the John Deere tractor and they were working on the engine.

00:33:23.200 --> 00:33:24.286
Isn't that interesting?

00:33:36.120 --> 00:33:41.623
And I'm not thinking about it because of green shirts, but it really was: I saw a green John Deere tractor and they were working on it.

00:33:48.160 --> 00:33:51.500
To be the best mechanic there is or the best aircraft mechanic, why not be the best at anything?

00:33:51.500 --> 00:33:59.853
All that you do, in word and in deed, we are to give all to the glory of God.

00:33:59.853 --> 00:34:02.810
All that we do, we do unto him.

00:34:04.400 --> 00:34:11.040
And Father, I thank you, Lord, that that's the kind of people we are in these last days.

00:34:11.040 --> 00:34:14.600
We don't just sit back and go, 'Well, you know what?

00:34:14.600 --> 00:34:25.911
' I told her we had one person who emailed and they had 666 in their email address.

00:34:27.267 --> 00:34:31.285
And I thought they're bold about being a devil worshiper.

00:34:31.285 --> 00:34:35.520
They're trying to tell us they're devil worshipers.

00:34:35.520 --> 00:34:37.019
I get that.

00:34:44.840 --> 00:34:45.060
But we're bold about being with Jesus.

00:34:51.149 --> 00:34:51.583
And we have maybe 777 in ours.

00:34:51.583 --> 00:34:53.729
I don't know.

00:34:53.729 --> 00:35:01.300
I guess that's God's number if they want to say 666 is theirs.

00:35:01.300 --> 00:35:04.491
But people are—you know what?

00:35:18.706 --> 00:35:19.870
You stand by what you believe.

00:35:19.880 --> 00:35:25.143
I guess if that's what you want to believe, you're believing the wrong thing.

00:35:25.143 --> 00:35:28.020
You're going to hell.

00:35:28.020 --> 00:35:39.040
But I want to tell you, I'm bold about Jesus just as much as you try to be bold about the devil.

00:35:39.040 --> 00:35:45.231
Or the people that try to come on here and tell everybody that they're giving five dollars because they're Muslim.

00:35:45.231 --> 00:35:51.873
We thank you for your five dollars, but you're still going to hell.

00:36:05.773 --> 00:36:06.520
I mean, I'm just saying if you don't know Jesus Christ, the only way you're ever going to get to heaven is through the Lord Jesus Christ.

00:36:19.832 --> 00:36:21.349
No Muhammad, not Buddha, not any other kind of false god.

00:36:31.310 --> 00:36:31.480
The only way to heaven is through the Lord Jesus Christ.

00:36:31.480 --> 00:36:37.920
Unless a man is born again, he cannot enter into the kingdom of God.

00:36:37.920 --> 00:36:40.160
Jesus is the only way.

00:36:43.060 --> 00:36:46.200
I don't care how much you come on and say, 'Hey, let me give you five dollars.

00:36:46.200 --> 00:36:52.610
' Put your name up and say, 'Allah is getting you to heaven.

00:36:52.610 --> 00:36:57.815
' Allah isn't getting you into heaven.

00:37:08.005 --> 00:37:08.200
I'm sorry, but it is not going to get you to heaven.

00:37:13.675 --> 00:37:18.693
To the man in New York saying he's going to put Islam in every household in America: good luck because you aren't doing it to mine.

00:37:18.693 --> 00:37:22.720
As for me and my house, we will serve the Lord.

00:37:25.400 --> 00:37:28.776
You aren't putting your garbage down my throat, telling me I've got to have Sharia law.

00:37:28.776 --> 00:37:36.867
We aren't having Sharia law up in here, Oklahoma or Texas.

00:37:36.867 --> 00:37:38.227
Your nonsense is nonsense.

00:37:38.680 --> 00:37:42.691
And the people will catch on to your lies, sir.

00:37:53.400 --> 00:37:53.950
And eventually they'll oust you just like they do everybody else.

00:37:53.950 --> 00:37:55.980
This is nonsense.

00:37:55.980 --> 00:37:58.000
'Well, we'll have Sharia law.

00:37:58.000 --> 00:38:02.783
' You aren't going to have any Sharia law up in here.

00:38:02.783 --> 00:38:04.360
We're a Christian nation.

00:38:04.360 --> 00:38:05.554
We're not Muslim.

00:38:05.554 --> 00:38:08.060
We've got to have a million christians.

00:38:08.060 --> 00:38:09.320
He called it Islamophobic.

00:38:09.320 --> 00:38:11.217
I said, 'We're not Muslim.

00:38:11.217 --> 00:38:13.440
We're not afraid of you.

00:38:17.040 --> 00:38:17.340
We don't have Islamophobia.

00:38:17.340 --> 00:38:19.943
We just know you.

00:38:19.943 --> 00:38:30.329
We know your stuff is trash and what you say is a lie.

00:38:33.520 --> 00:38:34.053
And who you're serving is a false god who's dead.

00:38:34.053 --> 00:38:49.820
We serve a risen savior and his name is Jesus Christ and he's seated at the right hand of the Father making intercession for me right now.

00:38:49.820 --> 00:38:51.070
Yours is not.

00:38:51.070 --> 00:38:57.813
He's in hell burning forever.

00:39:11.795 --> 00:39:12.030
That's where your god is.

00:39:12.030 --> 00:39:13.205
He's in hell.

00:39:13.205 --> 00:39:13.909
He's false.

00:39:13.909 --> 00:39:20.160
Our God is the only God and he reigns supreme over all of them.

00:39:20.160 --> 00:39:23.680
They're all false and it's all demonic spirits.

00:39:23.680 --> 00:39:34.260
And we have the risen savior, Jesus Christ, who died for you and he rose again for you.

00:39:42.693 --> 00:39:43.167
And he doesn't want you to go to hell.

00:40:02.811 --> 00:40:03.063
He wants you to get born again and get saved.

00:40:03.063 --> 00:40:05.966
But it's time people get bold.

00:40:05.966 --> 00:40:21.302
If they want to be bold about what they believe in their Sharia law, we have to become even bolder and have our cup overflowing with the word of God in these last days.

00:40:21.302 --> 00:40:33.775
If you don't stand for something, you're going to lose it all.

00:40:33.775 --> 00:41:00.080
You must stand as a believing believer in these last days or you're going to have that kind of trash being forced down your throat and your kids in school telling them this is the way to go.

00:41:00.080 --> 00:41:04.167
I beg to differ with you.

00:41:08.417 --> 00:41:20.926
I'm telling you folks, we're in a time like we've never seen before that the church has got to become more radical for Jesus and stand for something.

00:41:20.926 --> 00:41:35.846
The political correctness has got to end where, 'Well, we don't want to offend people because it's not politically correct to become bold.

00:41:35.846 --> 00:42:05.565
' Well, they're praying so loud on their loudspeaker and going in the background and the church gets in trouble if we turn up our stuff too.

00:42:05.565 --> 00:42:18.006
Well, we don't want to say it on social media because now you offend them and you're going to go to jail in Europe.

00:42:18.006 --> 00:42:37.720
A little bit more compromise because the church becomes a little bit more quiet, a little bit more passive, a little bit more weak.

00:42:37.720 --> 00:42:50.960
But I guarantee you that George Washington, if he were back right now and he saw where some things are, he would roll over in his grave.

00:42:50.960 --> 00:42:55.460
He'd go, 'Oh no.

00:42:55.460 --> 00:43:12.405
' Seriously, our founding fathers would literally have a fit and flip out for some of the stuff that's going on right now and say, 'What are you all doing?

00:43:12.405 --> 00:43:15.880
' and slap every single one of them.

00:43:15.880 --> 00:43:21.571
But yet the church goes, 'It's okay.

00:43:21.571 --> 00:43:24.505
' No, no, we've got to accept everybody.

00:43:24.505 --> 00:43:35.115
I'm not saying we don't pray for them and we love on them, but we don't accept the sin.

00:43:35.115 --> 00:43:37.780
What is it about acceptance?

00:43:37.780 --> 00:43:42.863
No, sin leads you to hell.

00:43:42.863 --> 00:43:47.075
People need to wake up.

00:43:47.075 --> 00:43:50.373
Sin leads you to hell.

00:43:50.373 --> 00:43:51.853
Period.

00:44:10.550 --> 00:44:11.420
People don't want to hear that.

00:44:11.420 --> 00:44:23.013
But I'm telling you now, I'm surprised I have 5,500 people on here right now.

00:44:23.013 --> 00:44:26.856
People get mad, want to leave.

00:44:26.856 --> 00:44:33.724
'Hey, I'm out of here because you tell me sin takes me to hell.

00:44:33.724 --> 00:44:35.671
' It's the truth.

00:44:43.640 --> 00:44:46.669
And it's my job to tell somebody what the word says and you don't want to hear it.

00:44:57.290 --> 00:44:58.060
That's fine.

00:44:58.060 --> 00:45:02.359
But at least I told you.

00:45:02.359 --> 00:45:08.382
Your blood's not on my hands.

00:45:08.382 --> 00:45:22.578
But it made me so upset when I heard his closing speech last night of what he said over the New York people and where he's at.

00:45:23.351 --> 00:45:24.640
And I thought, that's America.

00:45:24.640 --> 00:45:27.576
That's us.

00:45:27.576 --> 00:45:32.611
That's not too far from here.

00:45:32.611 --> 00:45:36.980
That's only a couple thousand miles away, but yet...

00:45:36.980 --> 00:45:40.600
Well, we don't want to speak out too much.

00:45:42.093 --> 00:45:51.280
And I thought, as he said, it sounds like a supervillain off a Batman movie.

00:45:51.280 --> 00:45:52.000
It did.

00:45:52.000 --> 00:45:54.879
It sounds like somebody in a Superman movie.

00:46:12.560 --> 00:46:12.720
You know, like whenever you hear the villain up there talking and he's telling all the people with his grandeur and he has the evil plan.

00:46:12.720 --> 00:46:32.168
Like Spider-Man, he has it behind him and he's the guy in the back planning some kind of mass evil plan to hurt everybody and he's talking about the City of Gotham and you're going, 'We've got a modern-day supervillain up there.

00:46:32.168 --> 00:46:37.225
' But this is not a movie.

00:46:37.225 --> 00:46:38.800
This is America.

00:46:38.800 --> 00:46:42.874
This is the land I love.

00:46:42.874 --> 00:46:48.217
This is the place I pray for every day of my life.

00:46:56.880 --> 00:46:57.429
And I thought, what are y'all thinking?

00:46:57.429 --> 00:46:59.075
They're not.

00:46:59.075 --> 00:47:05.940
They have a reprobate mind full of the devil.

00:47:05.940 --> 00:47:07.160
Why?

00:47:07.160 --> 00:47:09.610
Because the church isn't radical enough.

00:47:17.511 --> 00:47:17.716
They got scared and they shrunk back.

00:47:25.580 --> 00:47:32.580
And well, you know, it's not politically correct to always do that.

00:47:38.291 --> 00:47:38.600
And I'm just saying, well, a little leaven ruins the whole lump.

00:47:50.074 --> 00:47:51.960
A little leaven, just a little bit, and after a while, we see what happens up north.

00:48:00.987 --> 00:48:01.982
And I pray—that's why the Lord said to me, 'Brandon, it's trying to come down on Oklahoma.

00:48:01.982 --> 00:48:08.298
Remember my word that the Lord gave y'all through me.

00:48:08.298 --> 00:48:24.505
' He said it will have a dividing line from Altus, Oklahoma to Miami, and it will be divided with the next governor's race.

00:48:47.280 --> 00:48:47.536
It will be blue and red.

00:49:05.130 --> 00:49:06.060
It will be a fight to stay red.

00:49:06.060 --> 00:49:11.422
You must pray for Oklahoma.

00:49:11.422 --> 00:49:14.340
That's what he said.

00:49:14.340 --> 00:49:27.269
For a state that's predominantly red and has very moral values, all this will try to go blue in the next race.

00:49:29.394 --> 00:49:29.583
And I went, 'Very conservative.

00:49:29.583 --> 00:49:31.960
' And I thought, 'No way.

00:49:31.960 --> 00:49:34.980
We'll never see that.

00:49:34.980 --> 00:49:35.565
No way.

00:49:35.565 --> 00:49:37.480
' And the Lord's warning about it.

00:49:37.480 --> 00:49:38.555
He said, 'Pray.

00:49:38.555 --> 00:49:39.977
Pray over Arkansas.

00:49:39.977 --> 00:49:41.920
Pray over Louisiana.

00:49:41.920 --> 00:49:43.595
Pray over Texas.

00:49:43.595 --> 00:49:45.860
Pray over these states.

00:49:45.860 --> 00:49:58.253
Pray over this state that we remain the heartland of America, of the Bible Belt.

00:50:04.768 --> 00:50:05.376
And we stand for it.

00:50:05.376 --> 00:50:13.360
And we're radically born again in this area.

00:50:13.360 --> 00:50:21.848
And this is a place of refuge for the end times.

00:50:21.848 --> 00:50:37.846
' I'm telling you, I've seen the people by the millions here coming for the revivals.

00:50:37.846 --> 00:50:42.756
Stand for Jesus.

00:50:54.960 --> 00:50:55.416
We must stand for Jesus.

00:50:55.416 --> 00:51:08.720
As bold as they are for Muhammad, we must stand for Jesus.

00:51:08.720 --> 00:51:10.400
They're radical about their prayer.

00:51:10.400 --> 00:51:14.227
They're radical about what they believe.

00:51:14.227 --> 00:51:21.760
They treat their women, put them in head coverings, and they do all things.

00:51:21.760 --> 00:51:23.880
They're radical about what they believe.

00:51:23.880 --> 00:51:25.629
But we must become radical about Jesus.

00:51:46.400 --> 00:51:46.640
I'm not talking about being violent like they would be.

00:51:46.640 --> 00:51:56.870
I'm saying you must become radical about your belief and stand for what you believe.

00:52:07.855 --> 00:52:08.160
Jesus is Lord.

00:52:08.160 --> 00:52:10.760
Jesus is Lord over America.

00:52:10.760 --> 00:52:13.160
Jesus is Lord over Oklahoma.

00:52:13.160 --> 00:52:17.945
Jesus is Lord over Tulsa and Oklahoma City and Edmond.

00:52:17.945 --> 00:52:27.737
Jesus is Lord over Texas and Fort Worth and Dallas and wherever you are.

00:52:27.737 --> 00:52:30.000
Jesus is Lord.

00:52:47.871 --> 00:52:48.062
I proclaim it and I'm bold about it.

00:52:48.062 --> 00:52:49.018
Colorado Springs, Colorado.

00:52:49.018 --> 00:52:52.240
Jesus is Lord over Queensland, Australia.

00:52:52.240 --> 00:52:53.907
Jesus is Lord.

00:52:53.907 --> 00:52:55.620
Thank you, Father.

00:52:55.620 --> 00:53:00.320
Lord, we just thank you that you're Lord.

00:53:08.651 --> 00:53:09.046
And I thank you for that fire.

00:53:09.046 --> 00:53:22.440
I was seeing a man as I was driving by today and he was demon-possessed and he was off his rocker.

00:53:22.440 --> 00:53:26.970
I said, 'Father, I thank you for greater fire.

00:53:26.970 --> 00:53:29.960
I thank you for the greater fire for these people.

00:53:29.960 --> 00:53:31.914
' They need Jesus.

00:53:31.914 --> 00:53:48.200
They need help, boldness, and more confidence, more of that bulldog faith that when we touch people, they will get free by the power of the blood of Jesus, by what he did on that cross.

00:53:48.200 --> 00:53:55.200
Father, as he is, so are we in this world.

00:53:55.200 --> 00:54:00.995
Jesus Christ, the same yesterday, today, and forever.

00:54:10.700 --> 00:54:11.060
And if he was healing the sick 2,000 years ago, he'll heal the sick today because he's the same yesterday, today, and forever.

00:54:11.060 --> 00:54:14.233
But, Father, it's the anointing that destroys the yoke.

00:54:14.233 --> 00:54:16.186
It's the burden-removing, yoke-destroying power.

00:54:16.186 --> 00:54:19.880
It's the anointing that came to set the captives free.

00:54:20.640 --> 00:54:22.754
And that's what the people are needing right now.

00:54:26.840 --> 00:54:27.040
I thank you, Father.

00:54:27.794 --> 00:54:31.422
I thank you, Lord, that we're anointed and appointed for such a time as this.

00:54:31.422 --> 00:54:38.280
Every single person that's represented here tonight, Father, has that fire shut up in their bones.

00:54:45.040 --> 00:54:45.440
That Holy Ghost fire that's shut up in their bones.

00:54:45.440 --> 00:54:52.150
Father, that there's that fire, that Holy Ghost fire, that Holy Ghost presence.

00:54:57.100 --> 00:54:57.800
The greatest move of God is on this last generation, more than we've ever seen before.

00:54:57.800 --> 00:55:02.031
But it will be by the fire of the Holy Ghost.

00:55:02.031 --> 00:55:07.760
We thank you, Father, for a fresh touch of the fire.

00:55:07.760 --> 00:55:21.391
We thank you, Lord, for a fresh touch of the anointing of the Holy Ghost that you stir in the people, Father, that out of their belly shall flow rivers of living water.

00:55:21.391 --> 00:55:26.049
Lord, that we become bolder, yet not shrinking back in intimidation.

00:55:26.049 --> 00:55:32.166
We take authority over the spirit of intimidation over this generation.

00:55:32.166 --> 00:55:43.850
